Canada only. Must purchase a Handheld PC powered by Windows CE between March 1 
and June 30, 1999. Pick up the promotion mail-in rebate from your local reseller or 
print it off of our Web Site at www.microsoft.com/windowsce/hpc. &copy; 1999 Microsoft 
